Hey there,
Is this syntax OK for Makefile use? I'm only asking out of personal  
ignorance and because I'd use:
Kconfig:
config LZO1X_COMPRESS
	select LZO1X
	tristate
config LZO1X_DECOMPRESS
	select LZO1X
	tristate
config LZO1X
	tristate (or boolean??)
Makefile:
obj-$(CONFIG_LZO1X) += lzo1x/
Thanks,
Michael-Luke
